{"_path":"/councilor/service/s4040","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"爭取樂善國小通學步道改善計畫","description":null,"image":"/images/service/4040-1.jpeg","sequence":4037,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.1 加速宜居城市建設","link":"https://www.facebook.com/groups/a7xinlinkou/permalink/701684721936779/","author":"陳雅倫","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"陳雅倫"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-04-16T00:00:00.000Z","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"爭取樂善國小通學步道改善計畫"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"爭取樂善國小通學步道改善計畫"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"桃園市通學步道改善"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市通學步道改善"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市樂善國小的通學步道規劃是桃園市政府推動的「通學步道改善計畫」的一部分，旨在提升學童的通學安全和便利性。這項計畫由市府工務局負責，並與其他相關單位合作，進行跨部門的協調。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"該通學步道的設計重點包括："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"實體人行道"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：分隔人流與車流，確保學生行走的安全。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"家長接送區"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：增設避車彎和專屬接送區，減少交通混亂。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"無障礙設施"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：設置無障礙斜坡道和導盲磚，創造更友善的通行環境。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"擴大人行道淨寬"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：移除障礙物，提供更寬敞的行人空間。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"路口安全設施"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：加強路口的停等空間和行人保護措施，如庇護島等。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這些措施旨在逐步改善樂善國小周邊的通學環境，並在全市範圍內逐步推廣類似的改善計畫 ("},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/Taoyuan/breakingnews/4255391","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自由時報電子報"}]},{"type":"text","value":") ("},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/paper/1574893","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自由時報電子報"}]},{"type":"text","value":")。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"此外，該計畫也是市府「道路 2.0」補助計畫的一部分，意圖在未來的市區規劃中更廣泛應用，以提高學童的安全性和城市整體交通的便利性 ("},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://focusnews.com.tw/2023/09/531168/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"今傳媒 JNEWS"}]},{"type":"text","value":")。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"爭取作業說明"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"爭取作業說明"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善國小前方有一塊私人地，感謝里長、校長及地主的協助，讓樂善國小前方可以做完整的通學步道以及規劃接送區避車彎。這部分近期可以先行施工。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"另外，原市府規劃的方案（如圖）未將樂學路上的擋土牆納入，但雅倫認為舊有擋土牆及圍牆年久失修，我建議一併規劃打除，以現今的工法重做安全合適的圍牆，也讓出人行空間。並建議通學步道要串連到樂善社區，讓樂善國小及文德非營利幼兒園的孩子都可以安全上學！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4040-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4040-1.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4040-2.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4040-2.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"感謝雅倫！！ 期望現在難看的人行道能有更好的利用及成為接送兒童的安全區域！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4040-3.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4040-3.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雅倫爭取的樂善國小全區通學步道改善 如圖，目前也已送前瞻計畫，希望儘快核定儘快施作！！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4040-4.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4040-4.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4040-5.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4040-5.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"_20240809-樂善國小周邊通學步道準備開工"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2024/08/09 樂善國小周邊通學步道準備開工！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"下禮拜一工班正式進場，雅倫今日特別與各局處走訪兩校，做施工前的說明會～\n開學在即，希望趁暑假期間加緊腳步，施工期間也必須預留行人通道，降低對學生開學後的影響！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4040-6.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4040-6.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"爭取樂善國小通學步道改善計畫","depth":2,"text":"爭取樂善國小通學步道改善計畫","children":[{"id":"桃園市通學步道改善","depth":3,"text":"桃園市通學步道改善"},{"id":"爭取作業說明","depth":3,"text":"爭取作業說明"}]},{"id":"_20240809-樂善國小周邊通學步道準備開工","depth":2,"text":"2024/08/09 樂善國小周邊通學步道準備開工！"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s4040.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s4040.md","_extension":"md"}